		<title>Lastminute.com: le 10 regole per avere successo con le OTA sono 9</title>
		<link>http://lidiamarongiu.wordpress.com/2010/12/10/lastminute-com-le-10-regole-per-avere-successo-con-le-ota-sono-9/</link>
		<comments>http://lidiamarongiu.wordpress.com/2010/12/10/lastminute-com-le-10-regole-per-avere-successo-con-le-ota-sono-9/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 10 Dec 2010 15:14:22 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>lidiamarongiu</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Turismo 2.0]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[lastminute.com]]></category>
